# 1Ô∏è‚É£7Ô∏è‚É£ COMMON FAILURE POINTS TO AVOID

‚ùå Ignoring delivery feasibility in evaluation
‚ùå Assuming all suppliers can deliver equally
‚ùå No geographic risk modeling
‚ùå No historical delivery tracking
‚ùå Not factoring customs or border constraints
‚ùå Overreliance on supplier declarations

